@mark1900 we do not load hadoop libs via extension but always have them on the classpath of main druid process (mainly because of the custom hadoop versions we have, they are not available in maven and it was simpler to just have all on the classpath), so we will never see this issue anyway.
I'm not sure what change between 0.8.0 and 0.8.1 would cause this (I haven't had any time to repro it though, so not sure if this is really an issue or if there is something special about your setup)
I am on the druid IRC, ping me if you are there.
